title: 1924 Coupe de France Final
text: The 1924 Coupe de France Final was a <a href="soccer">football</a> match held at <a href="Stade%20Olympique%20Yves-du-Manoir">Stade Olympique</a>, <a href="Colombes">Colombes</a> on April 13, 1924, that saw <a href="Olympique%20de%20Marseille">Olympique de Marseille</a> defeat <a href="FC%20S%C3%A8te">FC Sète</a> 3–2 thanks to goals by <a href="Edouard%20Crut">Edouard Crut</a> (2) and <a href="Jean%20Boyer%20%28footballer%29">Jean Boyer</a>.
